Expressions	(parts in all caps are word-by-word translations)
Hello (to one)	igo hluf bo
    lit. YOU SEE I (I see you)
Hello (to many) igai hluf bo
    lit. YOU SEE I (I see you)
Thank you (to one)	igo xa dzifst
    lit. YOU ON VICTORY (victory on you)
Thank you (to many)	igai xa dzifst
    lit. YOU ON VICTORY (victory on you)
You're welcome	dzifst
    lit. victory	
Please	dzifst ab
    lit. VICTORY FOR for victory	
Sorry   ibo xa shezh
    lit. ME ON DEFEAT defeat on me	
Bye   Ppaeftto shaixae!
    lit. come / return again
Welcome   same as hello
	
Battle cries (regular words, but used as battle cries with elongated vowels at the end)
WAR!!!  rezh-AEAEAEAEAE
ATTACK!!!   saixsUUUUUUUU
Drown demons, poison snakes, and turn deons to suns     Roppaestosh Shae! Zhoxaesh Zhox! Shosh ri Shosh Aefstza Neft!
	
